{"tid":224667,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友遊戲","createTime":"2017-05-01T08:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T19:31:21.000Z","uid":48791,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d2975d8a7eb8d5b058549f0529b75b6d733858d","tid":224667,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-DbR8A0Acvco/WPBQxW6PPCI/AAAAAAAAgo0/OeVd3m9hLjsYFdunIXo12JyNJeh5N6u5QCLcB/s1600/%25E6%259C%258B%25E5%258F%258B%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%2588%25B2%2528%25E3%2583%2588%25E3%2583%25A2%25E3%2583%2580%25E3%2583%2581%25E3%2582%25B2%25E3%2583%25BC%25E3%2583%25A0%2529.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-DbR8A0Acvco%2FWPBQxW6PPCI%2FAAAAAAAAgo0%2FOeVd3m9hLjsYFdunIXo12JyNJeh5N6u5QCLcB%2Fs1600%2F%2525E6%25259C%25258B%2525E5%25258F%25258B%2525E9%252581%25258A%2525E6%252588%2525B2%252528%2525E3%252583%252588%2525E3%252583%2525A2%2525E3%252583%252580%2525E3%252583%252581%2525E3%252582%2525B2%2525E3%252583%2525BC%2525E3%252583%2525A0%252529.jpg&h=af74ae62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朋友遊戲 簡介 Friends Games Synopsis<br />\n《朋友遊戲》由 吉澤亮、內田理央、山田裕貴 主演的2017年日本電視劇。<br />\n<br />\n故事大綱<br />\n主人公是父母雙亡的貧窮少年片切友一，與班上另外4人是好友。一天，班上修學旅行的錢被偷，而偷錢的那個人正是好友5人組中的一個。此人因欠下2千萬的債務，希望好友一起幫忙還債而偷走了錢報名了朋友遊戲。雖然5人決定為了朋友參加遊戲，可事情遠沒有想像中的簡單。5人之間的友情將何去何從！？<br />\n<br />\n演員列表<br />\n片切友一／吉澤亮<br />\n沢良宜志法／內田理央<br />\n美笠天智／山田裕貴<br />\n四部誠／大倉士門<br />\n心木ゆとり／根本凪<br />\n東條レン／久保田悠来<br />\n<br />\n線上看:<a href=\"http://jp01.jplovetv.com/2017/04/friends-games-list.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjp01.jplovetv.com%2F2017%2F04%2Ffriends-games-list.html&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao8mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=d12524b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://jp01.jplovetv.com/2017/04/friends-games-list.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n套野係漫畫改編，岩岩睇完第一集劇情還原得唔錯，但我覺得D選角就唔係太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出完電視劇好似仲會出兩套電影版"},{"pid":"e8026abfe275f161